{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":709,"text":"Shah Rukh Khan: Be it Mumbai or Delhi,\nChennai or Kolkata,"},{"time":2598,"text":"all our big cities have\none great thing in common,"},{"time":5666,"text":"they happily welcome people from \nsmaller places arriving in search of work."},{"time":11970,"text":"What is also true is that\nthis warm welcome leads to consequences."},{"time":17450,"text":"Problems like housing\nin these cities are born."},{"time":20250,"text":"Today we have with us a human settlement\nexpert and researcher: Dr. Gautam Bhan,"},{"time":25533,"text":"who is re-imagining a solution\nto this increasing problem."},{"time":29650,"text":"He will share with us the new picture\nof urban India that he can see."},{"time":35026,"text":"TED Talks India New Thoughts\nwelcomes Dr. Gautam Bhan."},{"time":38788,"text":"Dr. Gautam Bhan, everyone."}]},{"cues":[{"time":39988,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":51570,"text":"Gautam Bhan: In this country,\nuntil a few years ago,"},{"time":53530,"text":"if you asked someone:"},{"time":55628,"text":"\"Where are you from?\""},{"time":57640,"text":"the answer would be\nDelhi, Mumbai, Kolkata."},{"time":61250,"text":"You'd immediately ask again:"},{"time":64370,"text":"\"Where do you belong?\""},{"time":67410,"text":"Until recently in India,\nnobody was from a city;"},{"time":72170,"text":"people only migrated to the city."},{"time":74250,"text":"This is changing."},{"time":76570,"text":"Urbanization is changing India,"},{"time":80290,"text":"but are our cities prepared?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":83690,"text":"Let's assume you were born somewhere else."},{"time":86170,"text":"Your parents worked as laborers all day."},{"time":91389,"text":"Then you too would have come\nto a city for progress."},{"time":94130,"text":"Or maybe, like it happens today,\nyou were born in the city itself."},{"time":97450,"text":"One day you go out looking\nfor an accommodation in the city,"},{"time":102010,"text":"to buy or maybe just to rent."},{"time":105810,"text":"Will you be able find an affordable home?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":110312,"text":"The government says we are falling\nshort of at least 20 million homes."},{"time":115370,"text":"20 million homes,\nthat's 100 million people."},{"time":119170,"text":"And this is not the shortage of <i>3 BHKs</i>\n(bedroom hall kitchen)."},{"time":122086,"text":"95 percent of the shortage"},{"time":124652,"text":"is for people earning\n10 to 15,000 rupees per month."},{"time":128113,"text":"Will you be able to find\nan affordable home in this budget?"},{"time":132810,"text":"If this happened with you,\nwhat would you do?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":135053,"text":"Home is not a car\nor some sort of jewellery."},{"time":137490,"text":"Home is food and clothes."},{"time":139530,"text":"Nobody can live without it."},{"time":142010,"text":"If you couldn't find a home\nin a city to either buy or rent,"},{"time":145930,"text":"you too would be driven to do\nwhat most people end up doing."},{"time":150330,"text":"Make a home wherever possible."},{"time":154010,"text":"You too would make a <i>settlement.</i>"},{"time":156690,"text":"The government may keep calling it a <i>slum,</i>"},{"time":159359,"text":"but like the people living there,"},{"time":161610,"text":"I too will call it a settlement."}]},{"cues":[{"time":164130,"text":"One hundred million are not homeless."},{"time":167450,"text":"They have homes."},{"time":169251,"text":"Homes they built on their own."},{"time":171874,"text":"But most of these homes\nare in settlements."},{"time":175641,"text":"This is the truth\nof an affordable home in India."},{"time":179570,"text":"The homes in settlements are cheap,\nbut not sturdy."},{"time":183130,"text":"The homes outside are sturdy,\nbut not cheap."}]},{"cues":[{"time":187167,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":190598,"text":"We will have to lay the foundation\nof a new thought from here itself."},{"time":194802,"text":"A settlement is not a problem;\nit is a solution."},{"time":199370,"text":"We just have to make it secure and sturdy."},{"time":202810,"text":"To fulfill the shortage\nof 20 million homes"},{"time":205893,"text":"you cannot make 20 million\n25 square foot flats,"},{"time":211210,"text":"and neither should you be making them."}]},{"cues":[{"time":213410,"text":"For example take the Karnataka government."},{"time":217010,"text":"They have a very good record in this."},{"time":221650,"text":"By 2020, Karnataka needs\n2.6 million homes."},{"time":226170,"text":"In the last ten years they have managed\nto make 350,000 homes."},{"time":230962,"text":"Even if a government tries\nwith complete sincerity,"},{"time":235130,"text":"it cannot fulfill this need\nin the next couple of lifetimes."},{"time":238730,"text":"If we do not make new homes,"},{"time":241330,"text":"then what is the next solution?"},{"time":243650,"text":"How to make a settlement secure?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":245810,"text":"Firstly, eviction needs to be stopped."},{"time":248890,"text":"Bulldozing needs to be stopped."},{"time":251090,"text":"Never has that resulted\nin progress in the past,"},{"time":253339,"text":"nor will it in the future."}]},{"cues":[{"time":254923,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":259290,"text":"We have to start believing that\nthe laborers who build and run the city"},{"time":264490,"text":"have a right over the land of that city."}]},{"cues":[{"time":266950,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":270130,"text":"I know you are thinking"},{"time":272051,"text":"that settlements are made\non illegally captured land,"},{"time":276690,"text":"but capturing of land never happens\nin the dead of the night."},{"time":280836,"text":"Whether the land belongs\nto the government or not,"},{"time":283490,"text":"a settlement is never formed secretly."},{"time":286010,"text":"It is inhabited over time."},{"time":287650,"text":"The government also agrees that"},{"time":289210,"text":"the settlements in our cities have been\nthere for over 10, 20, 30, even 40 years."},{"time":295410,"text":"What kind of\nillegally captured land is this,"},{"time":297690,"text":"which was ignored for 30 years"},{"time":300330,"text":"and suddenly a day before eviction\nis declared illegal?"},{"time":305050,"text":"A settlement can easily accommodate\n15 to 60 percent of a city's population"},{"time":310010,"text":"by using just one, two\nor maximum ten percent of the land."},{"time":315210,"text":"Can such a huge number of people not have\na right over this small bit of land?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":319520,"text":"A city's progress is often measured\nby the cost of its land."},{"time":323131,"text":"How do you ascribe a cost to the life\nof a person living on a piece of land?"},{"time":326970,"text":"A settlement is not asking you\nfor shiny homes;"},{"time":330410,"text":"all it's asking for is basic necessities:"},{"time":333122,"text":"electricity, roads, water,\ntoilets and drainage."},{"time":338370,"text":"We call this <i>upgradation.</i>"},{"time":343201,"text":"Here's an example of upgradation."},{"time":345305,"text":"In Ahmedabad, they started a program"},{"time":347370,"text":"where for ten years, 44 settlements were\npromised there wouldn't be any eviction."},{"time":351643,"text":"Only a promise."},{"time":353050,"text":"Nothing written, no documents."},{"time":355810,"text":"And basic necessities\nwere provided to them."},{"time":358170,"text":"In ten years that slum changed into\na locality, a place, a world of its own."},{"time":364850,"text":"The government didn't have to build\neven a single new home."}]},{"cues":[{"time":367838,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":372610,"text":"Thailand launched this program\nat national scale,"},{"time":377230,"text":"benefiting 100,000 people in 137 cities."},{"time":381674,"text":"And every person was given the right\nto live over that land."},{"time":386130,"text":"But pay attention here."},{"time":387798,"text":"Not the right to sell,\nbut the right to live there,"},{"time":391330,"text":"use it, settle on it."},{"time":394890,"text":"The whole world knows now\nthat to move forward,"},{"time":399570,"text":"we cannot remove settlements."},{"time":401970,"text":"We can only advance when we think of ways\nto make settlements secure and sturdy."},{"time":407290,"text":"But just one thing."},{"time":408650,"text":"If we know it, then why doesn't it happen?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":411450,"text":"To apply this new thinking to settlements,"},{"time":414050,"text":"we, that is you and me,\nneed to look deep within"},{"time":418890,"text":"and get rid of the disgust, disrespect\nand apprehensions that we have."},{"time":426490,"text":"Actually I should not be standing\nhere in front of you today."},{"time":430490,"text":"A person from the settlement who lives\nthere should be standing here."},{"time":437410,"text":"But if someone like that came here,\nyou wouldn't have listened to him."},{"time":442025,"text":"You are listening to me, because you think\nI am not from a settlement."},{"time":446828,"text":"This is the very thought\nthat needs to be changed."}]},{"cues":[{"time":450131,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":450916,"text":"(Applause)"},{"time":459414,"text":"SRK: Thank you very much.\nThank you, Dr. Gautam Bhan."},{"time":461662,"text":"Thanks a lot."}]},{"cues":[{"time":463572,"text":"Please tell me, you just gave\nan example of Thailand"},{"time":466431,"text":"and the big thing there is"},{"time":468807,"text":"the homes are for people\nto settle in, not to sell."},{"time":472556,"text":"They cannot be used for sale."},{"time":475370,"text":"Is there a similar thought process\nor program in our country too,"},{"time":479979,"text":"inspired by your talks\nand those of people around you?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":482669,"text":"GB: I wouldn't say by me,"},{"time":484610,"text":"but by the people movement\nwho are fighting for rights in the city."},{"time":490331,"text":"That is making a difference."},{"time":492175,"text":"For instance, in Odisha"},{"time":493415,"text":"the Chief Minister, Mr. Patnaik,\nannounced the same scheme:"},{"time":498382,"text":"that all the people in settlements\nwill have rights over that land."}]},{"cues":[{"time":503640,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":506730,"text":"And I think this scheme\nshouldn't be called populism;"},{"time":511105,"text":"it should be called an economic\ndevelopment strategy."},{"time":513930,"text":"Because economic development does not\nhappen from the top, but from the bottom."}]},{"cues":[{"time":518126,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":522410,"text":"SRK: I too promise"},{"time":524160,"text":"I will only say settlements,\nand not slums, ever again. 100 percent."}]},{"cues":[{"time":528624,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":531970,"text":"Dr. Bhan you came here and said such\nwonderful things."},{"time":535112,"text":"There is a song. I will not sing it,\nas I am a terrible singer."}]},{"cues":[{"time":538850,"text":"GB: I too am a terrible singer."}]},{"cues":[{"time":540443,"text":"SRK: But we can't keep shut also,\nbecause we are saying wonderful things."},{"time":543580,"text":"(laughter)"},{"time":544329,"text":"So we will just say it."},{"time":545307,"text":"Slowly the heart will find settlement."},{"time":548079,"text":"GB: Slowly the heart will find settlement."},{"time":550604,"text":"SRK: Only then will life be filled\nwith love and fun times."}]},{"cues":[{"time":553206,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":554460,"text":"Ladies and gentlemen, Dr. Gautam Bhan.\nThank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":556778,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":557635,"text":"Thank you very much."}]},{"cues":[{"time":558601,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}